3: The nanny rushes toward the bawling child, while in the shadows, a sharp blade flashes into sight—
You! You killed my mommy! Go away!
A malicious glint flashes in the darkness, and the child rams a knife into the nanny's form. Her metal shell crumbles, vital fluid flooding out.
The lights come on to reveal the caretaker's form, curled up tight around the child, knife in her abdomen. On her torso rests the weapon aimed at the child, plunged deep into her own body.
...! Punishing Virus levels surging in the caretaker android.
I took care of some of those with my arrows.
